  "text": "In literature, the duration of the studies ranges between 2 and 7 years with a prior preparation period. [CITATION_1] One of the important limitations of our study is the short duration of the study, which could have contributed to the observed low compliance ratio. We would have thought that to assess the increment in the compliance ratio accurately the implementation should follow a process.",
